name: Harley Walter
description: I am a well grounded person who misses being in a relationship. I’m very open, charming, loving, understanding and honest. I’ve got good sense of humor and I enjoy traveling, cruises, way itching movies. I have a big heart and I am ready to give all my heart to the right woman. I’m looking for that cherishing relationships where I can feel blessed that I have found the right one for me and we can share everything in life with no secret and enjoy life together to the fullest..
